Khoa in t Vin thng- Trng i hc Khoa hc t nhin

Bi 5: THIT K LC IIR

Nhm: Ca02

H v tn: Nguyn Anh Tun MSSV: 20200399

Mục đích:¶

  • Xc nh c cc thng s b lc cn thit k
  • Thit k c b lc IIR
  • Phn tch tch tn hiu trc v sau lc

Tm tt l thuyt :

thit k lc IIR ta s dng cc phng php sau:

  1. S dng hm signal.iirfilter() $b, a = iirfilter(N, Wn, rp=None, rs=None, btype='band', analog=False, ftype='butter', output='ba')$
    Trong :

    N: Bc lc
    Wn: L tn s gc chun ha c gi tr t 0 -> 1. n v l rad/mu (lc s) rad/s (lc tng t). Khi tn s ct bng tn s nyquist th Wn = 1.
    rp: dn sng ti a di qua (dB) (i vi lc Chebyshev v elliptic)
    rs: dn sng ti thiu di chn (dB) (i vi lc Chebyshev v elliptic)
    btype: Loi lc: 'bandpass, lowpass, highpass, bandstop
    analog: Chn loi lc s hay lc tng t mc nh l lc s
    ftype: Loi lc IIR cn thit k

  • Butterworth : butter
  • Chebyshev I : cheby1
  • Chebyshev II : cheby2
  • Cauer/elliptic: ellip
  • Bessel/Thomson: bessel

output : Mc nh l to ra cc h s b, a

  1. S dng hm signal.iirdesign() $$b, a = signal.iirdesign(wp, ws, gpass, gstop, analog=False, ftype= 'ellip', output = 'ba')$$ Trong :

    wp, ws: l tn s chun ha di qua v tn s ct chun ha di chn. V d:

  • Lowpass: wp = 0.2, ws = 0.3
  • Highpass: wp = 0.3, ws = 0.2
  • Bandpass: wp = [0.2, 0.5], ws = [0.1, 0.6]
  • Bandstop: wp = [0.1, 0.6], ws = [0.2, 0.5]

gpass: dn sng di qua (dB)
gstop: dn sng di chn (dB)
analog: Chn loi lc s hay lc tng t mc nh l lc s
ftype: Loi lc IIR cn thit k

  • Butterworth : butter
  • Chebyshev I : cheby1
  • Chebyshev II : cheby2
  • Cauer/elliptic: ellip
  • Bessel/Thomson: bessel

output : Mc nh l to ra cc h s b, a

  1. Thit k theo kiu Matlab Cc hm c c php ging trong Matlab
    V d:

  • Thit k lc Butterword:
    N, Wn = signal.buttord(wp, ws, gpass, gstop, analog=False)
    b, a = signal.butter(N, Wn, btype='low', analog=False, output='ba')

  • Thit k lc Chebyshev loi 1 N, Wn = signal.cheb1ord(wp, ws, gpass, gstop, analog=False)
    b, a = signal.cheby1(N, rp, Wn, btype='low', analog=False, output='ba')

  • Tng t i vi Chebyshev loi 2, Elliptic

b, a = signal.iirfilter(N = 4, Wn = [0.4, 0.8], rs=60, btype='band',
                        analog=False, ftype='cheby2')
w, H = signal.freqz(b, a, worN=512, whole = False)
plt.plot(w/np.pi, 20 * np.log10(abs(H)))
plt.title('p ng tn s lc di qua Chebyshev loai II')

plt.ylabel('Amplitude [dB]')

Chng trnh thit k lc IIR thp qua Chebyschev loi 2, bc 8, tn s ct l 10Hz, rs = 60. p dng b lc ln tn hiu x.
a. V p ng tn s b lc
b. V tn hiu vo v ra trn 1 hnh

In [3]:
sampleRate = 100 #Tn s ly mu
nSamples = 400   #S mu
t = np.arange(nSamples)/sampleRate #Khong thi gian
x = np.cos(2*np.pi*0.5*t) + 0.2*np.sin(2*np.pi*2.5*t+0.1) + \
        0.2*np.sin(2*np.pi*15.3*t) + 0.1*np.sin(2*np.pi*16.7*t + 0.1) + \
            0.1*np.sin(2*np.pi*23.45*t+.8)
nyquistRate = sampleRate/2 #Tn s Nyquist
cutOffFreq = 10 #Hz
#Vit tip chng trnh  y
N = 8
wC = cutOffFreq/nyquistRate # Tn s ct 
b, a = signal.iirfilter(N, wC, rs=60, btype='low',analog=False, ftype='cheby2')
y = signal.lfilter(b, a, x)
w, H = signal.freqz(b,a, worN=512)
plt.subplot(2,1,1)
plt.plot((w/np.pi)*nyquistRate, abs(H), linewidth=2)
plt.title('p ng tn s') 
plt.xlabel('Tn s (Hz)')
plt.ylabel('Bin ')
plt.subplot(2,1,2)
plt.plot(t, x, linewidth=2, label = 'Tn hiu x')
plt.title('Tn hiu vo v ra') 
plt.xlabel('Thi gian')
plt.ylabel('Bin ')
plt.plot(t, y, 'r-', linewidth=2, label = 'Tn hiu y')
plt.legend()#Hin th ghi ch
plt.subplots_adjust(top=1.5, hspace=0.5)

b_fir = signal.firwin(15, 0.5, window="triang") 
w, h = signal.freqz(b_fir, 1, worN=1024)

b_iir, a = signal.iirfilter(15, 0.5, rp=0.5, rs=50, btype='low',analog=False, ftype='butter')
w, H = signal.freqz(b_iir,a, worN=1024)
plt.title('p ng tn s thp qua IIR Butterworth v FIR ')
plt.plot(w/np.pi, 20 * np.log10(abs(h)))
plt.plot(w/np.pi, 20*np.log10(abs(H)),'r')
plt.legend(["Lc FIR", "Lc IIR"])
plt.ylim(-100,0)

#a Phn tch ph ca 2 tn hiu
from scipy.io import wavfile
from scipy import fftpack as fft
from scipy import signal
import IPython.display as ipd #Thm th vin  play Audio
file_goc= 'violin_origional.wav'
file_nhieu= 'violin_noise.wav'
fs, s_goc = wavfile.read(file_goc)
ipd.Audio(s_goc, rate=fs)       #Pht Audio
fs, s_nhieu = wavfile.read(file_nhieu)
ipd.Audio(s_nhieu, rate=fs)       #Pht Audio
nyquistRate = fs/2
#Phn tch ph
w, S_goc = signal.freqz(s_goc, 1, worN=512)
w, S_nhieu = signal.freqz(s_nhieu, 1, worN=512)
plt.subplot(2,1,1)
plt.plot((w/np.pi)*nyquistRate, np.abs(S_goc))
plt.title("Ph ca tn hiu gc")
plt.xlabel("Tn s(Hz)")
plt.ylabel("Bin ")
plt.subplot(2,1,2)
plt.plot((w/np.pi)*nyquistRate, np.abs(S_nhieu))
plt.title("Ph ca tn hiu nhiu")
plt.xlabel("Tn s(Hz)")
plt.ylabel("Bin ")
plt.subplots_adjust(top = 1, hspace = 0.5)
